Defendant in custody.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of 1st degree sexual assault of a child.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 04-14-14 at 2:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $1,000.00 cash with the conditions that he have no contact with the victim, E.L.M., age 5 or Jesseka Clay or any residence they reside in, 1829 28th Street, Two Rivers, WI and no contact with anyone under the age of 18, other than incidental contact, or in any residence where a person under the age of 18 resides in.  Bail furnished and the defendant is released from custody.
